    "summary": "The user asks for safe, high-achieving school districts in North Carolina, eventually probing whether \"safety\" and \"stability\" are euphemisms for racial segregation. The assistant provides general recommendations and later addresses the link between racial demographics and school performance by noting correlations between white-dominated areas and well-funded systems.",
